ol.li: CR3 Reload: The hardware root is swapped.
Implicit Flush: Changing CR3 typically flushes non-global TLB entries.
Virtual Aliasing: Both processes use Virtual Address 0x1000, but map to distinct physical frames (0x07 vs 0x2A).
